00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:41.240
Feliz cumpleaños.

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:52.799
Lo lamento.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:56.480
Soy tan estúpido.

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:09.960
